---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services - Skief Labs" description="Data Intelligence and Sales Acceleration services for B2B companies. AI-powered outbound systems and automated data pipelines.">
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-linen pt-12 pb-16 md:pt-16 md:pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <!-- Left: Text -->
        <div>
          <h1 class="page-hero-title heading-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.8rem] text-navy-900 mb-6 leading-[1.1] uppercase">
            Two services.<br />Both done<br />seriously.
          </h1>
          <div class="page-hero-body space-y-4 text-navy-900/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
            <p>Skief Labs works on two specific problems for B2B companies:<br />getting the right data, and building the outbound systems that<br />turn it into pipeline.</p>
            <p>We don't offer a menu of services. We don't take on work<br />outside these two areas.</p>
            <p>If either problem is real for your business, it's worth a<br />conversation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="page-hero-cta mt-8">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book a 30-minute discovery call</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Right: Image -->
        <div class="page-hero-image relative">
          <img src="/images/sk4.jpg" alt="The outbound process" class="w-full rounded-lg object-contain shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_#CFFF15]" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICE ONE: DATA INTELLIGENCE -->
  <section id="data-intelligence" class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Section Header -->
      <div class="mb-20">
        <div class="inline-block border border-navy-900 text-navy-900 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_#001233] mb-6">Service One</div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] text-navy-900 mb-4 leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em]">
          Data Intelligence
        </h2>
        <p class="text-navy-900/60 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl">
          The data your team needs — built, enriched, and delivered automatically.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- The Problem -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-16 mb-24">
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">
          <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-neon rounded-full"></div>
              <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-lg text-navy-900 font-medium tracking-wider">The Problem</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-5 text-navy-900/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          <p>Most B2B teams have a data problem they've quietly learned to work around.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 border-l-2 border-navy-900/20 pl-6">
            <li>Lists that are months out of date before they're used.</li>
            <li>Research that pulls senior people away from higher-value work.</li>
            <li>Enrichment that's incomplete, inconsistent, or both.</li>
            <li>Decisions made on inputs no one fully trusts.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-navy-900 font-bold">This isn't a tools problem.<br />It's a systems problem.</p>
          <p>The fix isn't another data subscription. It's a pipeline that finds, enriches, scores, and delivers the right information automatically — so the work stops requiring people.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What We Build -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-16 mb-24">
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">
          <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-neon rounded-full"></div>
              <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-lg text-navy-900 font-medium tracking-wider">What We Build</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
          <!-- Card 1: Research & Scraping -->
          <div class="build-card bg-linen rounded-lg p-7 border-2 group">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-linen flex items-center justify-center text-navy-900 flex-shrink-0">
                <iconify-icon icon="solar:server-square-update-linear" width="24" height="24"></iconify-icon>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-navy-900 text-sm font-semibold whitespace-nowrap">Research & Scraping Pipelines</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              The data your team currently sources by hand — contacts, companies, roles, signals — collected automatically from the sources that matter for your specific use case. Continuously refreshed, not exported once and forgotten.
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Card 2: AI Enrichment -->
          <div class="build-card bg-linen rounded-lg p-7 border-2 group">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-linen flex items-center justify-center text-navy-900 flex-shrink-0">
                <iconify-icon icon="solar:magic-stick-3-linear" width="24" height="24"></iconify-icon>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-navy-900 text-sm font-semibold whitespace-nowrap">AI-Powered Enrichment & Scoring</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Raw data isn't useful. We build enrichment logic that layers context, qualifies records, and scores outputs — so what reaches your team is clean, relevant, and ready to act on.
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Card 3: Agentic Research -->
          <div class="build-card bg-linen rounded-lg p-7 border-2 group">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-linen flex items-center justify-center text-navy-900 flex-shrink-0">
                <iconify-icon icon="solar:cpu-linear" width="24" height="24"></iconify-icon>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-navy-900 text-sm font-semibold whitespace-nowrap">Agentic Research Workflows</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              For complex research that currently consumes senior time, we build AI agents that gather, structure, and summarize — in the exact format your team uses to make decisions.
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Card 4: Signal & Trigger -->
          <div class="build-card bg-linen rounded-lg p-7 border-2 group">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-linen flex items-center justify-center text-navy-900 flex-shrink-0">
                <iconify-icon icon="solar:radar-linear" width="24" height="24"></iconify-icon>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-navy-900 text-sm font-semibold whitespace-nowrap">Signal & Trigger Identification</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Hiring activity. Funding events. Technology changes. Leadership moves. We surface the buying signals relevant to your ICP automatically, so your team acts on fresh intelligence instead of stale assumptions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Who This Is For -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-16 mb-24">
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">
          <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-neon rounded-full"></div>
              <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-lg text-navy-900 font-medium tracking-wider">Who This Is For</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 max-w-2xl text-navy-900/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-5">
          <p>Data Intelligence engagements serve teams where the quality of inputs directly determines the quality of everything downstream.</p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 bg-neon rounded text-navy-900 text-xs flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p><span class="font-bold text-navy-900">Marketing teams</span> using data for account targeting, segmentation, and campaign intelligence.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 bg-neon rounded text-navy-900 text-xs flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p><span class="font-bold text-navy-900">HR and talent teams</span> using it for candidate sourcing, market mapping, and competitive research.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 bg-neon rounded text-navy-900 text-xs flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p><span class="font-bold text-navy-900">Growth teams</span> using it to feed sales systems with reliable, continuously refreshed data.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Not a fit box -->
          <div class="rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 mt-6 border-l-4" style="background-color: #f9f6f0; border-left-color: #001233;">
            <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-sm leading-relaxed"><span class="font-bold text-navy-900">Not a fit?</span> This is not a fit if you need a quick list or a one-time export. This is for teams with a recurring data need that has outgrown what manual effort or off-the-shelf tools can sustain — and where the cost of bad data is real and measurable.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What Good Looks Like -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 mb-20">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-neon rounded-full"></div>
            <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-lg text-navy-900 font-medium tracking-wider">What Good Looks Like</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-navy-900/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            <p>When a Data Intelligence system is working, your team stops talking about data quality.</p>
            <p>They trust the inputs. Decisions get faster. The research backlog<br />disappears. The people who used to spend hours finding<br />information spend that time using it instead.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 80-90% Stat -->
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="rounded-2xl px-10 py-10 text-center w-full" style="background-color: #f9f6f0;">
            <p class="font-serif text-6xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight" style="color: #001233;">80–90<span style="color: #CFFF15;">%</span></p>
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mt-3 text-black">Reduction in manual data handling</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- How This Engagement Works -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 mb-12">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-neon rounded-full"></div>
            <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-lg text-navy-900 font-medium tracking-wider">How This Engagement Works</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-navy-900/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            <p>Every Data Intelligence engagement starts with the discovery call. From there, we scope the work properly before anything is built.</p>
            <p>We build to a fixed scope with full documentation and handoff<br />at the end.</p>
            <p>Some clients extend into an ongoing arrangement where we continue running and refreshing the system. Others take it and run it themselves. Either way, you own it completely.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="bg-navy-900 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 w-full">
            <p class="text-neon text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-semibold mb-4">Investment</p>
            <p class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl text-linen mb-4">System builds from <span class="text-neon">$5,000.</span></p>
            <p class="text-linen/70 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">Fixed scope. Full documentation. Handoff at the end. You own it completely.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary w-full text-center block">Book a 30-minute discovery call</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICE TWO: SALES ACCELERATION -->
  <section id="sales-acceleration" class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Section Header -->
      <div class="mb-20">
        <div class="inline-block border border-navy-900 text-navy-900 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_#001233] mb-6">Service Two</div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] text-navy-900 mb-4 leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em]">
          Sales Acceleration
        </h2>
        <p class="text-navy-900/60 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl">
          More pipeline. Without more headcount.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- The Problem -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-16 mb-24">
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">
          <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-neon rounded-full"></div>
              <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-lg text-navy-900 font-medium tracking-wider">The Problem</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-5 text-navy-900/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          <p>Most B2B outbound fails for a reason that has nothing to do with the product, the market, or the team.</p>
          <p>It fails because the system underneath is fragile.</p>
          <p>Manual list building. Inconsistent personalization. Follow-up that depends on someone remembering. No visibility into what's working until it's too late to fix it.</p>
          <p>The result is a lot of effort producing unpredictable results — and a team that's busy but not productive.</p>
          <p class="text-navy-900 font-bold">We fix the system. Then we run it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What We Do -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-16 mb-24">
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">
          <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-neon rounded-full"></div>
              <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-lg text-navy-900 font-medium tracking-wider">What We Do</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
          <!-- Card 1: Outbound System Design -->
          <div class="build-card bg-linen rounded-lg p-7 border-2 group">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-linen flex items-center justify-center text-navy-900 flex-shrink-0">
                <iconify-icon icon="solar:compass-linear" width="24" height="24"></iconify-icon>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-navy-900 text-sm font-semibold whitespace-nowrap">Outbound System Design</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Before a single message is sent, we design the full targeting logic, data sources, personalization framework, and sequence architecture.
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Card 2: Clay-Powered Targeting -->
          <div class="build-card bg-linen rounded-lg p-7 border-2 group">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-linen flex items-center justify-center text-navy-900 flex-shrink-0">
                <iconify-icon icon="solar:target-linear" width="24" height="24"></iconify-icon>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-navy-900 text-sm font-semibold whitespace-nowrap">Clay-Powered Targeting</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              We use Clay as the data backbone — building dynamic lead sources, enrichment waterfalls, and scoring logic that ensures every contact your team reaches is the right one.
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Card 3: Multi-Channel Sequences -->
          <div class="build-card bg-linen rounded-lg p-7 border-2 group">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-linen flex items-center justify-center text-navy-900 flex-shrink-0">
                <iconify-icon icon="solar:chat-round-dots-linear" width="24" height="24"></iconify-icon>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-navy-900 text-sm font-semibold whitespace-nowrap">Multi-Channel Sequences</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Email and LinkedIn, working together. Touchpoints designed around actual buyer behavior and intent signals — not generic cadences copied from a playbook.
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Card 4: Done-For-You Operation -->
          <div class="build-card bg-linen rounded-lg p-7 border-2 group">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-linen flex items-center justify-center text-navy-900 flex-shrink-0">
                <iconify-icon icon="solar:rocket-2-linear" width="24" height="24"></iconify-icon>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-navy-900 text-sm font-semibold whitespace-nowrap">Done-For-You Operation</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              We run the outbound. Research, enrichment, personalization, sequencing, inbox management, and continuous optimization — handled by us. Your team focuses on the conversations.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Who This Is For -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-16 mb-24">
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">
          <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-neon rounded-full"></div>
              <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-lg text-navy-900 font-medium tracking-wider">Who This Is For</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 max-w-2xl text-navy-900/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-5">
          <p>Sales Acceleration is built for B2B founders, sales leaders, and growth teams who know their outbound should be working harder — and who are honest about the fact that the current approach isn't scaling.</p>
          <p>We work with a small number of Sales Acceleration clients at a time. That's not a positioning line — it's how we maintain the quality that makes the work effective.</p>
          <!-- Not a fit box -->
          <div class="rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 mt-6 border-l-4" style="background-color: #f9f6f0; border-left-color: #001233;">
            <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-sm leading-relaxed"><span class="font-bold text-navy-900">Not a fit?</span> This is not a fit for teams looking for a short campaign or a quick blast. This is for teams who want a reliable outbound motion they can build on.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What Good Looks Like -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 mb-20">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-neon rounded-full"></div>
            <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-lg text-navy-900 font-medium tracking-wider">What Good Looks Like</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-navy-900/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            <p>When Sales Acceleration is running well, outbound stops feeling like a gamble.</p>
            <p>Your team has consistent conversations in the calendar. The pipeline becomes predictable. The manual research and personalization that used to take hours happens automatically.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 3-5x Stat -->
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="rounded-2xl px-10 py-10 text-center w-full" style="background-color: #f9f6f0;">
            <p class="font-serif text-6xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight" style="color: #001233;">3–5<span style="color: #CFFF15;">x</span></p>
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mt-3 text-black">More outreach capacity, same headcount</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- How This Engagement Works -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 mb-12">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-neon rounded-full"></div>
            <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-lg text-navy-900 font-medium tracking-wider">How This Engagement Works</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-navy-900/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            <p>Sales Acceleration begins with a pilot project — a defined scope, fixed price, and clear deliverable.</p>
            <p>The pilot covers ICP definition, data sourcing and enrichment via Clay, sequence architecture and copy, system build and launch, and first weeks of live execution.</p>
            <p>Most clients move to an ongoing monthly retainer after the pilot. There is no obligation to continue beyond the pilot.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="bg-navy-900 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 w-full">
            <p class="text-neon text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-semibold mb-4">Investment</p>
            <p class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl text-linen mb-4">Pilot projects from <span class="text-neon">$10,000.</span></p>
            <p class="text-linen/70 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">Ongoing retainer from $3,000/month. No obligation to continue beyond the pilot.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary w-full text-center block">Book a 30-minute discovery call</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- A NOTE ON AI -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Heading block -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-block">
            <!-- Label with line, left-aligned to heading text -->
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-navy-900"></div>
              <p class="subhead-condensed text-xs text-navy-900 tracking-[0.2em]">Our Approach</p>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] text-navy-900 mb-3 leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em] text-center">
              A note on AI & automation
            </h2>
            <!-- Line right-aligned to heading text -->
            <div class="flex justify-end">
              <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-navy-900"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-10"></div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-navy-900/70 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-center">
          <p>You'll notice we don't list AI and automation as a service.<br />That's intentional.</p>
          <p>AI and automation are how we build — not what we sell. Every Data Intelligence pipeline runs on automation. Every Sales Acceleration system uses AI for enrichment, personalization, and research at scale.</p>
          <p>We don't offer automation as a standalone product because the technology is never the point. The point is the outcome — cleaner data, more pipeline, less friction for the people doing the work.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Callout box -->
        <div class="flex items-stretch gap-4 mt-10">
          <div class="w-0.5 bg-navy-900 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-sm italic leading-relaxed py-1 text-left">If you're looking for a partner who uses automation and AI seriously — embedded in systems designed to solve real problems — we might be exactly right.</p>
          <div class="w-0.5 bg-navy-900 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE DON'T DO -->
